OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781722095
OL,3,CResidents at religious community deny
OL,4,Cobstructing police during raids
OL,6,FA total of 25 people were due to
OL,7,Fappear at South Cheshire Magistrates'
OL,8,FCourt, on 17 June, charged with public
OL,9,Forder offences alleged to have
OL,10,Fhappened when the raids were carried
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FAnnika Livermore, prosecuting, told
OL,14,Fthe court residents obstructed
OL,15,Fofficers from getting into rooms at
OL,16,FWebb House, the group's headquarters,
OL,17,Fsome by linking arms to try and stop
OL,18,Fthem getting past.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781722095
OL,3,CResidents at religious community deny
OL,4,Cobstructing police during raids
OL,6,FShe said defendant Dareem Charles was
OL,7,Falleged to have kicked at shields of
OL,8,Fpolice officers and thrown items,
OL,9,Fwhile Marc Ferreira was alleged to
OL,10,Fhave grabbed hold of an officer while
OL,11,Fhe was making an arrest.
OL,13,FOldest defendant Ramazan Demirovic,
OL,14,F59, was witnessed pushing past
OL,15,Fofficers and wedging himself against a
OL,16,Fdoorframe, Ms Livermore said.
OL,18,FShe added: "The defendant was then
OL,19,Fseen to lash out with his arms and
OL,20,Fpush an officer to the face."
OL,26,@zD@LOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
