OL,3,CResidents at religious community deny
OL,4,Cobstructing police during raids
OL,6,FLaure Delogne, who spoke through a
OL,7,FFrench interpreter, was accused of
OL,8,Fhiding in a bush when police officers
OL,9,Fentered the site, the court heard.
OL,11,FThe defendants, aged between 18 and 59
OL,12,Fwith addresses in Crewe, were brought
OL,13,Finto court individually, with the
OL,14,Fhearings listed to go on until the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,17,FMany wore black clothing and some wore
OL,18,Fblack beanie hats.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
