CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781722095
OL,3,CResidents at religious community deny
OL,4,Cobstructing police during raids
OL,6,FCheshire Police said the defendants
OL,7,Fwere of nationalities including
OL,8,FBritish, French, Belgian, Iranian,
OL,9,FEgyptian and American.
OL,11,FOutside the court building a handful
OL,12,Fof protesters gathered, using their
OL,13,Fphones to film defendants as they
OL,14,Farrived.
OL,16,FDistrict Judge Ian Barnes granted the
OL,17,Fdefendants unconditional bail until
OL,18,Ftheir trials, listed for dates in
OL,19,FApril 2027.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
